Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.10,0:01:49.65,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛が愛を「重過ぎる」って理解を拒み
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.82,0:01:54.45,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憎しみに　変わって行く前に…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.59,0:01:56.42,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何もかもそうだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.54,0:02:01.44,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,バツの悪い事情にはいつも蓋して
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.55,0:02:04.27,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,食わせ物のリアル
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.38,0:02:06.60,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歪んだジレンマ時代で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.75,0:02:10.36,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約束したはずの二人さえ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.50,0:02:14.84,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,気付かず通り過ぎて行く
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.51,0:02:22.46,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壊しあって　解り合ったことも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.64,0:02:24.27,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,置き去りにした
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.39,0:02:27.71,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,これが成れの果てなの？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.84,0:02:32.25,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認めないで　立ち向かったときも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.86,0:02:38.46,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,落ちて行く時のイメージから逃げ出せずに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.60,0:02:43.20,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ah　何度でも探し出すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.30,0:02:49.95,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君の目　その手の温もりを
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.17,0:02:55.29,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛はいつも私を傷つけるだけ…って君はつぶやいて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.40,0:02:59.95,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信じる事が怖くて泣いたんだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.14,0:03:02.20,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弱さを知って強くなれ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.35,0:03:05.96,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐れず信じることで
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.08,0:03:10.98,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本当の愛を知るだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.10,0:01:49.65,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛說愛「過於沉重」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.82,0:01:54.45,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在轉變成恨之前　把它拒絕於心門之外…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.59,0:01:56.42,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬物皆是如此吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.54,0:02:01.44,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是把不合時宜的事隱藏起來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.55,0:02:04.27,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是冒牌貨的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.38,0:02:06.60,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在扭曲了的窘迫時代
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.75,0:02:10.36,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連本應定下約定的兩人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.50,0:02:14.84,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都會毫無察覺地擦肩而過
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.51,0:02:22.46,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那開始崩壞但曾經互相理解的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.64,0:02:24.27,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將其撇下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.39,0:02:27.71,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是所謂的末路嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.84,0:02:32.25,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心中不服　想與之對抗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.86,0:02:38.46,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要從當初墮落的印象中逃離開去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.60,0:02:43.20,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　就算歷經千百次也要找出
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.30,0:02:49.95,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的雙眸　你手中的余溫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.17,0:02:55.29,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小聲嘟囔著「愛總是讓我遍體鱗傷…」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.40,0:02:59.95,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因畏懼堅信不疑的事而哭過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.14,0:03:02.20,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道軟弱才能變強
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.35,0:03:05.96,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要害怕堅信不疑地走下去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.08,0:03:10.98,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才是愛的真諦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.01,0:00:03.91,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}（14年前  聯合領地  國際大學）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.85,0:00:06.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拜讀了你的畢業論文
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.49,0:00:11.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無人機戰鬥的戰術理論及損失規模的預測
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.53,0:00:15.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢業後果真想做戰術預報員嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.80,0:00:16.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正是這麼打算的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.20,0:00:18.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.39,0:00:23.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會留在大學跟隨埃夫曼教授繼續MS的研究
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.52,0:00:26.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過真有你的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.78,0:00:30.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年僅17歲就從這裡畢業了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.96,0:00:32.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還差得遠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.31,0:00:35.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起卡蒂簡直望塵莫及
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.30,0:00:38.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡蒂？那個戰術預報的天才啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.27,0:00:43.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在接連發表的戰術中  成功處理了七次紛爭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.82,0:00:47.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳言AEU邀請她過去享受校官待遇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.55,0:00:48.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是我的目標
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.18,0:00:53.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不能阻止戰爭  那至少能利用戰術速戰速決
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.66,0:00:56.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把損失減到最小  來拯救人們的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.79,0:01:01.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想成為像卡蒂那樣的戰術預報員
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.42,0:01:03.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你絕對可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.73,0:01:06.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢業就見不到面了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.48,0:01:08.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點寂寞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.41,0:01:13.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是對比自己小五歲的女生說的話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.35,0:01:16.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…算是吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.92,0:01:19.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麗莎  我讀了你的畢業論文
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.63,0:01:21.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.31,0:01:22.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  卡蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.99,0:01:25.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次和你見面會是在戰場上了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.75,0:01:28.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的話我可不想和你為敵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.65,0:01:31.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬內金…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.21,0:01:39.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼會在A-LAWS…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.87,0:01:41.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.02,0:03:19.90,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,0)}#10 天之光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.10,0:03:32.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校  蘇伊爾王國的動向如何
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.90,0:03:34.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在還毫無變化
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.06,0:03:37.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我覺得總有一天會改變的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.49,0:03:42.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反對中東重製計劃的蘇伊爾國力不能小覷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.27,0:03:45.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果蘇伊爾做出行動
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.47,0:03:47.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別的國家必定會紛紛跟從
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.23,0:03:49.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了阻止這種事態發生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.43,0:03:53.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦政府決定派遣獨立治安維持部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.36,0:03:54.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,派A-LAWS？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.99,0:03:59.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦軍已駐紮在蘇伊爾的國境線了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.59,0:04:02.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此舉可認為是對蘇伊爾的牽制吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.93,0:04:07.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個國王的話  面對聯邦是不會退讓的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.74,0:04:10.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然擁有世界第一的信息產業
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.30,0:04:13.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但中東全境通訊處於如此封鎖狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.12,0:04:16.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那信息也就無作作為了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.29,0:04:23.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由於聯邦的信息操作  中東的現狀更不為世界所知
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.32,0:04:25.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘇伊爾軍事能力如何
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.03,0:04:26.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然瞭解得不是很詳細
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.06,0:04:29.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎擁有中東第一的軍備
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.90,0:04:31.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在聯邦設立之前
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.44,0:04:35.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依靠稀有金屬和信息產業成為中東第一富國
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.26,0:04:36.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真魯莽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.76,0:04:39.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算這樣也絕不是聯邦的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.03,0:04:41.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.62,0:04:47.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是蘇伊爾  這4年中也開發不出性能超過聯邦的新型兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.07,0:04:50.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但就算我們出手相助也是杯水車薪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.81,0:04:53.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一個辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.39,0:04:56.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把蘇伊爾所持有的信息
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.73,0:04:59.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即聯邦對中東施行的惡政
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.41,0:05:02.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過我們卡塔隆的網路組織向全球發佈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.07,0:05:04.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輿論有了反對的呼聲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.63,0:05:07.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦對中東也就不敢妄為
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.54,0:05:08.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.62,0:05:11.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來  就有與蘇伊爾進行交涉的必要了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.77,0:05:14.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,池田  能與王室聯繫上嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.95,0:05:18.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託當記者時期的朋友應該…沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.65,0:05:19.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.54,0:05:22.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了中東…不  是為了世界
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.81,0:05:24.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.77,0:05:36.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席琳  阿扎提斯坦情況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.62,0:05:38.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,國民都怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.25,0:05:40.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從發表建立了臨時政府後
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.64,0:05:42.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就沒有什麼吸引眼球的報道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.77,0:05:46.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信息管制也完全依照聯邦的意願
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.49,0:05:48.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算想去看看阿扎提斯坦的狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.82,0:05:51.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,國境線也被聯邦軍封鎖了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.94,0:05:53.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直束手無策
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.35,0:05:54.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.98,0:05:55.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗娜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.69,0:06:00.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要重建阿扎提斯坦只有打倒聯邦一條路
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.40,0:06:04.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要戰鬥啊  作為公主的你有這個義務
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.79,0:06:07.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊  戰爭只能引發更多的戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.74,0:06:12.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認為人民能在用武力奪回的阿扎提斯坦上安居樂業嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.70,0:06:14.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你想忍氣吞聲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.52,0:06:16.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們已是亡國奴了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.62,0:06:18.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席琳  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.71,0:06:26.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  你什麼也別做就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.28,0:06:31.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我來戰鬥  不這樣做就不能奪回祖國
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.86,0:06:39.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那  我現在能理解了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.17,0:06:43.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去了故鄉…克魯吉斯的你的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.11,0:06:48.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仿佛自己的安身之處漸漸消失似的…這種失落感
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.03,0:06:54.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了這種心情  為何你還能戰鬥？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.87,0:06:59.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據觀察班的報告
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.04,0:07:04.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Being的宇宙船極有可能前往拉格朗日3
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.38,0:07:07.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由於林特少校接到特殊任務
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.39,0:07:10.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此追擊Gundam的任務由你來完成
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.42,0:07:11.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.23,0:07:12.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,增援也準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.92,0:07:15.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我期待你能為傑江中校報仇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.58,0:07:22.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九條…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.45,0:07:29.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米里奧！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.41,0:07:33.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那次事件成為了她心中永遠的芥蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.07,0:07:39.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此便倒向宣揚以根除戰爭為理念的Celestial Being嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.27,0:07:43.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢至極
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.01,0:07:46.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事只是愚蠢的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.99,0:07:49.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紛爭不可能從這世界上消失
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.33,0:07:56.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不就是為了防止戰事延長才當上戰術預報員的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.03,0:08:00.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校  我給您拿飯來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.81,0:08:01.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別私自進來！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.88,0:08:08.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對布林格下達了攻擊命令
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.89,0:08:13.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會怎麼接招呢？Celestial Being
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.53,0:08:23.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各傳感器  全部正常
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.83,0:08:26.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粒子供給規定值確認
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.28,0:08:29.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿扎提斯坦被…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.75,0:08:33.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的國家…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.57,0:08:34.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗娜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.09,0:08:37.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿里·阿爾·沙謝斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.74,0:08:40.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都沒有改變
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.32,0:08:42.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我也一事無成…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.54,0:08:45.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,E傳感器有反應
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.81,0:08:47.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有機影接近
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.02,0:08:49.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人  是A-LAWS嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.98,0:08:51.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.01,0:08:53.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.37,0:08:55.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.53,0:08:58.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了  某種危險的…東西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.06,0:09:02.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某種危險的…東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.74,0:09:05.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接近的機體速度達到了78千秒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.24,0:09:07.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這麼快
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.32,0:09:10.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵機居然只有一架？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.17,0:09:13.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arios和Seravee還在修理中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.20,0:09:16.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam緊急出發  狙擊敵機
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.22,0:09:18.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OO  先行出發
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.61,0:09:32.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.97,0:09:36.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搭載了偽太陽爐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.67,0:09:44.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是A-LAWS！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.52,0:09:48.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種機動性…又是新型機嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.29,0:09:56.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.51,0:09:57.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN Field？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.94,0:09:59.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦居然有能用Field的機體
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.55,0:10:16.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能用TRANS-AM的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.37,0:10:19.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那  沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.95,0:10:25.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那台新機型  居然壓倒了OO
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.33,0:10:30.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.05,0:10:34.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.22,0:10:36.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵機撤退了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.17,0:10:38.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣也太快了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.33,0:10:42.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回收Gundam之後  以最快速度前往拉格朗日3
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.00,0:10:43.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.39,0:10:46.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  敵人這是出的哪一招？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.90,0:10:49.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要告訴我們他們的軍隊已經擺好了陣型
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.66,0:10:51.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也向我們展示了新型機的性能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.83,0:10:54.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是所謂的牽制和警告
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.51,0:10:57.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來更加需要O-Raizer了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.53,0:10:58.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.96,0:11:01.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是馬內金的佯攻嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.34,0:11:07.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對沒錯  那架新型機的駕駛員是改革者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.55,0:11:10.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掌握了吠陀的他們能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.65,0:11:14.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也能開發使用GN Field的機體
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.62,0:11:16.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.74,0:11:17.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特瑞亞？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.90,0:11:19.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.38,0:11:21.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.75,0:11:23.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不說出他們的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.95,0:11:27.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…是猶豫了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.49,0:11:32.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,林特少校  情況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.41,0:11:36.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照預定順利進行中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.86,0:11:39.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整理好情況就向我報告
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.22,0:11:41.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我直接指揮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.68,0:11:42.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.85,0:11:45.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好看著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.96,0:11:48.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與統一政府作對的傢伙們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.28,0:11:52.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們將遭遇到的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.52,0:11:54.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是天降之雷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.94,0:11:56.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是神之審判
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,=========================
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.52,0:12:11.93,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（拉格朗日3  資源衛星群）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.60,0:12:13.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艙門打開
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.32,0:12:20.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激光傳感器與托勒密同步
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.96,0:12:31.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密  降落
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.69,0:12:33.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3  2  1
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.96,0:12:36.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦舷對接完成
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.21,0:12:38.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,固定用機械臂開始對接
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.43,0:12:42.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同步艙門對接完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.61,0:12:50.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等你們很久了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.11,0:12:54.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽  我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.26,0:12:57.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米蕾娜  過得還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.09,0:12:58.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.55,0:13:00.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才  好像在叫媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.54,0:13:01.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.85,0:13:02.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.03,0:13:06.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  你們是第一次見吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.25,0:13:07.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我妻子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.61,0:13:09.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琳達·瓦斯提
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.26,0:13:09.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真年輕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.99,0:13:11.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是犯罪哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.56,0:13:12.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.73,0:13:14.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩笑就此打住
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.40,0:13:15.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.16,0:13:19.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密和Gundam的補給和維修能不能快些
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.25,0:13:21.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.23,0:13:23.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-LAWS的部隊正在這片空域展開
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.94,0:13:28.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還以為這裡的偽裝很完美的  明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.45,0:13:32.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是補給和整備最少也要5天
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.69,0:13:33.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.61,0:13:34.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒見過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.98,0:13:38.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面  我是重新開始活動的同時
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.03,0:13:41.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被Celestial Being撬來的亞琉·利塔娜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.38,0:13:42.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撬來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.34,0:13:43.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.53,0:13:45.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王留美介紹來的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.01,0:13:47.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞琉很厲害的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.56,0:13:51.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不僅是宇宙物理學  MS工程學  還是再生治療的權威
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.70,0:13:55.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還會駕駛艦艇  做飯  外加還是個大美人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.85,0:13:58.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣  相當優秀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.31,0:14:00.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.67,0:14:10.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,池田發來的加密電文
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.37,0:14:12.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘇伊爾那邊好像同意了會談
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.44,0:14:14.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  他們同意了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.57,0:14:17.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會談就由我去吧  這裡的指揮就交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.13,0:14:19.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.37,0:14:21.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保險起見帶上護衛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.84,0:14:23.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我會的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.51,0:14:26.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是紅色的車子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.36,0:14:27.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.82,0:14:28.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.17,0:14:31.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘇伊爾被壞人盯上了是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.36,0:14:35.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要去打擾公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.24,0:14:40.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉  因為這孩子是來自蘇伊爾的  一直非常的不安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.07,0:14:46.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼大家不能和平相處呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.63,0:14:49.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  我也是這麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.72,0:14:53.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以得想出個讓大家和平相處的辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.40,0:14:55.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一起吃飯就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.20,0:14:58.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個點子很棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.52,0:14:59.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.83,0:15:03.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其它還有什麼別的方法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.90,0:15:09.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起玩  一起唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.24,0:15:10.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.13,0:15:12.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有讓大家互相看看自己寶貴的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.40,0:15:14.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.02,0:15:17.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.73,0:15:26.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是O-Raizer
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.13,0:15:31.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這部機體有控制Twin-Drive系統的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.80,0:15:33.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有對TRANS-AM的增幅機能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.80,0:15:34.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊的機體呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.66,0:15:38.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arios用的支援機 GN-Archer
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.66,0:15:38.41,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（GN-Archer：GNR-010A）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.90,0:15:41.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN-Archer
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.42,0:15:44.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始測試咯  刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.80,0:15:45.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.72,0:15:50.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉格朗治3裡居然有這種大規模的基地
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.04,0:15:57.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.40,0:16:01.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道如何是好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.04,0:16:05.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我的錯  很多人被奪去了性命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.37,0:16:07.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必須為犯下的罪孽有所償還
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.34,0:16:13.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是戰鬥  殺人這種事  我怎麼也…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.75,0:16:15.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做不到是很自然的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.86,0:16:22.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  不做點什麼  力所能及的事也…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.42,0:16:26.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  能冒昧地問一句嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.64,0:16:27.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.90,0:16:31.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你接下來還準備和他在一起嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.36,0:16:33.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  只要阿里路亞還在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.55,0:16:36.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使會被捲進戰爭裡也…？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.33,0:16:41.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾經是軍人  也有了這種覺悟
